Name: Depression Test
Description:
The authors of this test have learned a great deal about depression over the past few
decades. Much of this research has focused on the biological underpinnings of depression, and this work has led to a number of
new and effective medications. And while these advances have
undoubtedly helped to improve the quality of life for countless
people, a number of people, including yours truly, are concerned that the biological view of depression has been oversold.
Pass this test to find out, how depressed you are
